# UVHM Modifier                                                                                                                  #
# As this is now it does nothing else other than double exp from UVHM BUT you can alter it to your                               #
# Choice to make UVHM more Challenging or Less challenging. THIS AFFECTS ONLY UVHM not TVHM OR NORMAL.                           #
# Allright so in order to change Health/Shield of normal and/Or badasses Find first " (MinEffectiveLevel=61 "                    #
# After that Alter EnemyHealthMultiplier , BadassEnemyHealthMultiplier ,EnemyShieldStrengthMultiplier To your Liking             #
# You can do the same for (MinEffectiveLevel=50 but it is not reccomended due to you Having less skills at that point.           #
#                                                                                                                                #
# This can Create A PSEUDO OP8 mode if modify health of enemies accordingly. I am unsure of the exact values but                 #
# lets say the enemy has a 55% resist at op8 and the op8 weapons have 250%% more dmg than their op0 Counterpart                  #
# (I checked this with plump seeker(magsize) 72 was 670k while op8 was 1782k. OFC enemies have 8 lvls more health                #
#                                                                                                                                #
# Bassically i dont know the Math behind OP8 yet But when i do ill release a Pseudo OP8 UVHM for now tweak it to                 #
# your likings.                                                                                                                  #
##################################################################################################################################

